\forall a,b\in G'
f(a+_nb)=e^{2\pi i(a+_nb)/n}
f(a)f(b)
f(a+_nb)={\large e^{\large 2\pi i(a+_nb) \over n} = e^{\large \frac{2\pi i a}n + {\frac{\large 2\pi i b}n}} = e^{\large\frac {2\pi i a}n} \cdot e^{\large\frac{2 \pi i b}n}}= f(a)(b)
